#NewSong2025 #NewHindiSong #RomanticSong #EmraanHashmi #YamiGautam #EmraanYami #HindiSong #HindiNewSong #NewRomanticSong #NewHindiSong2025 #EmraanHashmiNewSong #YamiGautamNewSong #RomanticSongHindi #HindiSong2025 #BetaabDil #SaritDutta

‚ÄúBetaab Dil‚Äù is a heart-touching romantic Hindi song that brings back the golden era of 90s Bollywood music. Sung and composed by Sarit Dutta, this soulful melody beautifully captures the emotions of love, longing, and separation. The heartfelt lyrics by Dr. Uma Naveen Mehta paint a timeless picture of a betaab (restless) heart waiting for its beloved.

If you miss the charm of classic love songs, ‚ÄúBetaab Dil‚Äù will take you straight back to that nostalgic era of melody and emotion.

üéß Experience ‚ÄúBetaab Dil‚Äù ‚Äî A Pure Hindi Romantic Love Song
Close your eyes, feel the rhythm, and let this song remind you of the beautiful simplicity of true love. Perfect for anyone who believes in eternal romance and misses the soulful tunes of the 90s

üëâ Don‚Äôt forget to LIKE, SHARE & SUBSCRIBE for more soulful music.

Subscribe : https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCWj7oD9SuDcGciiBQT9BQuw?sub_confirmation=1
__________________________________________________

Song Credits
Song : Betaab Dil
Singer : Sarit Dutta
Music Composer : Sarit Dutta
Lyrics : Dr Uma Naveen Mehta
Backing Vocals : Subhajit Das
Music Produced, Mixed & Mastered by Sarit Dutta @ Rivertone Studio
__________________________________________________

Lyrics:-

Hum chahe itna hi 
Ab tera saath ho
Kya tune kabhi ye jana
Kitna dard hai mujhko

Bekhudi mein chal pade hai
Khudko hi ab mitane
Mere kadam rukte nahi 
Teri galiyon me aane se

Deewangi ki had se jyada
Hum karte hai ye pyaar tumko
Ankhon mein teri yaadein wo leke
Betaab dil chahe tujhko

Baaton ne teri
Mujhko saari raat jagaya
Sanson ne teri
Mujhko yu apna banaya

Koi lamha nahi hai mera
Jisme tu nazar na aaya
Na hamne koi khata ki
fir kyu tune di hai saja

Deewangi ki had se jyada
Hum karte hai ye pyaar tumko
Ankhon mein teri yaadein wo leke
Betaab dil chahe tujhko

snippet.title: One Direction - Night Changes (Lyrics)
snippet.description:
One Direction - Night Changes
Stream/Download:

(Lyrics):
[Verse 1: Zayn & Liam]
Goin' out tonight, changes into somethin' red
Her mother doesn't like that kind of dress
Everything she never had, she's showin' off
Drivin' too fast, moon is breakin' through her hair
She's headin' for somethin' that she won't forget
Havin' no regrets is all that she really wants

[Chorus: All & Harry]
(Ooh) We're only gettin' older, baby
(Ooh) And I've been thinkin' about it lately
(Ooh) Does it ever drive you crazy
(Ah-ah-ah) Just how fast the night changes?
(Ooh) Everything that you've ever dreamed of
(Ooh) Disappearin' when you wake up
(Ooh) But there's nothin' to be afraid of
(Ah-ah-ah) Even when the night changes
(Ooh) It will never change me and you

He's waitin', hides behind a cigarette
Heart is beatin' loud and she doesn't want it to stop
Movin' too fast, moon is lightin' up her skin
She's fallin', doesn't even know it yet
Havin' no regrets is all that she really wants

Tune in to all your favorite Bhakti songs and mantras on the Saregama Bhakti App.
Download now: https://sarega.ma/bhakti_yt

Saregama is India's oldest music label and has a never ending library of the most popular devotional songs, bhajans, aartis and puja vidhis. Saregama Bhakti is focussed on bringing you quality devotional and spiritual content sung by the legends of Bollywood, Devotional and Spiritual genre like Lata Mangeshkar, Jagjit Singh, Anup Jalota, Hari Om Sharan, Suresh Wadkar and many more. Right from Bhajans, Pooja Vidhis, Gurbani, Sai Bhakti we have it all available on your channel to help to enhance your divine experience and connect with the almighty at a new level.

What is Roblox? ROBLOX is an online virtual playground and workshop, where kids of all ages can safely interact, create, have fun, and learn. It‚Äôs unique in that practically everything on ROBLOX is designed and constructed by members of the community. ROBLOX is designed for 13 to 18 year olds, but it is open to people of all ages. Each player starts by choosing an avatar and giving it an identity. They can then explore ROBLOX ‚Äî interacting with others by chatting, playing games, or collaborating on creative projects. Each player is also given their own piece of undeveloped real estate along with a virtual toolbox with which to design and build anything ‚Äî be it a navigable skyscraper, a working helicopter, a giant pinball machine, a multiplayer ‚ÄúCapture the Flag‚Äù game or some other, yet-to-be-dreamed-up creation. There is no cost for this first plot of virtual land. By participating and by building cool stuff, ROBLOX members can earn specialty badges as well as ROBLOX dollars (‚ÄúRobux‚Äù). In turn, they can shop the online catalog to purchase avatar clothing and accessories as well as premium building materials, interactive components, and working mechanisms.

snippet.title: Creedence Clearwater Revival - Have You Ever Seen The Rain (Fan Celebration Version)
snippet.description:
We are celebrating your comments for the official Have You Ever Seen The Rain music video. Thank you for supporting CCR! 

Watch the official Have You Ever Seen The Rain music video: https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=u1V8YRJnr4Q

Follow Creedence Clearwater Revival:
https://www.youtube.com/@TheOfficialCCR
https://instagram.com/theofficialccr
https://tiktok.com/@theofficialccr
https://facebook.com/ccr
https://twitter.com/theofficialccr

Listen to ‚ÄúCCR: Chronicle - The 20 Greatest Hits‚Äù: https://ffm.to/ccr-chronicle

Visit the CCR store:
https://ccr.concord.com/products/

Subscribe to the CCR Newsletter: https://manage.kmail-lists.com/subscriptions/subscribe?a=Ut6Y6V&g=WyE6eZ

About Creedence Clearwater Revival: 
Creedence Clearwater Revival‚Äôs 1968 self-titled debut album introduced the world to guitar-playing brothers John and Tom‚ÄØFogerty, drummer Doug Clifford, and bassist Stu Cook, four young men out of El Cerrito in the San Francisco Bay Area. Though they emerged in a place and time where trippy psychedelic visions were the order of‚ÄØthe day, CCR bucked the trends and instead tapped into a rich, traditional seam of American music that connected to blues, country, rockabilly, gospel, folk and R&B.‚ÄØ‚ÄØ‚ÄØ 

During their short time together as a band (1968 ‚Äì 1972), the band enjoyed an unparalleled period of creativity lead by singer, songwriter, arranger John Fogerty. They‚Äôve sold close to 100 million records, releasing 14 Top 10 hits. They also managed to play over 150 tour dates around the world, including a headlining spot at Woodstock.

Creedence Clearwater Revival‚Äôs canon has become a part of the Great American Songbook. Fogerty penned songs like ‚ÄúBad Moon Rising,‚Äù ‚ÄúDown on the Corner,‚Äù ‚ÄúFortunate Son,‚Äù ‚ÄúHave You Ever Seen the Rain,‚Äù ‚ÄúProud Mary,‚Äù ‚ÄúBorn on the Bayou,‚Äù ‚ÄúTravelin‚Äô Band‚Äù and ‚ÄúUp Around the Bend‚Äù have been ingrained into pop culture ‚Äî not just as rock staples, but as classic standards.

With so many memorable songs that continue to grace our radio waves, television and movie screens, plus lyrics that still resonate today, Creedence Clearwater Revival is, truly, America‚Äôs greatest rock ‚Äôn‚Äô roll band.

#ccr #creedenceclearwaterrevival #haveyoueverseentherain
